\begin_layout Standard
These populations were not identified to have cryptic relatedness or had
 cryptic relatedness removed 
\series bold
[citation difficult (pptx file posted online KGP website) ftp://ftp.1000genomes.eb
i.ac.uk/vol1/ftp/phase1/analysis_results/supporting/cryptic_relation_analysis/Neme
